propel.core.collections.maps.combinational
Class AvlTreeList<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>

java.lang.Object
  propel.core.collections.maps.combinational.AvlTreeList<TKey,TValue>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<KeyValuePair<TKey,TValue>>, IListMap<TKey,TValue>, ReifiedMap<TKey,TValue>
public class AvlTreeList<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IListMap<TKey,TValue>

A type-aware AVL-tree-backed map holding values which are accessible by key as well as a list-style index. This map does not allow null keys to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new AvlTreeList<String, Object>(){}; -OR- new AvlTreeList<String, Object>(String.class, Object.class);
